description: WEAU's Joel Hibbard profiles Memorial High School Junior and now GRAMMY-Nominated Pianist and Composer Geoffrey Keezer. He has collaborated with acclaimed artists such as Diana Krall, Wayne Shorter, Art Blakey, Joshua Redman and recently with Chris Botti and Sting.
